                p 
                  span(style="color:blue; text-decoration:underline") Read more
            div(class="overlay")



      div(class="col-lg-6")
        div(class="img-container")
          a(href="code-ghana" class="plain")
            div.row
              div(class="col-lg-6 col-md-5")
                img(class="fit", src="images/code-woman.jpg")
              div(class="col-lg-6 col-md-7")
                  h3 Coding Classes in Ghana
                  p(style="font-size:20px") Creating the best online coding lessons in Africa.
            div(class="overlay")

      div(class="col-lg-3 col-md-5")
        img(class="fit", src="images/ethiopia-food.png")
      div(class="col-lg-3 col-md-7")
        h3 Community Lunch Promoting Science in Ethiopia
        p(style="font-size:20px") How I got 3000 dollars stuck in Ethiopia, and let an Ethiopian student use it to do a project important to him.

      div(class="col-lg-3 col-md-5")
        img(class="fit", src="images/alphasheet-python.png")
      div(class="col-lg-3 col-md-7")
        h3 Alphasheets: One Sheet to Rule Them All
        p(style="font-size:20px") Making the first spreadsheet that supports Python and R commands directly in-sheet.
